      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ibbi-Suen , the powerful king , the beloved of Inana : Saĝ-Enlila , steward of Inana , nueša - priest of Enlil , child of Lugal-engardug , steward of Inana , is your servant ."
